## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Bazaar has the following requirements:

* For disconnected environments, a container registry like [Harbor](https://network.pivotal.io/products/harbor-container-registry)
  is needed to manage images.
* [Docker](https://www.docker.com/)
* The [PKS CLI](https://docs.pivotal.io/runtimes/pks/cli/index.html)

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* Bazaar dedicated-instances provision an IaaS load balancer for ingress to each instance.


